
                   <p style="text-align: center">
                       <b>Title:</b> You can establish baselines for your system by recording the normal levels of various operational values. In the
future, you can compare current values to these baselines to help detect and resolve abnormal values.<br>
                       <b>Bounding box:</b> x1=134, y1=262, x2=1566, y2=1917
                   </p>
